hopobject.body:
EMBINUX is a embedded software and solution development initiative of SQLStar International Inc, USA which is a wholly owned subsidiary of SQLStar International Limited, India. EMBINUX is involved in cutting edge research and development in the area of embedded Linux.Its products and solutions ranges form software platform development, BSP , protocol stacks, cross compiler, custom tools, middleware components, multimedia framework upto application development.

-- http://embinux.com http://www.sqlstar.com
